comment: After communicating with the Replay Center, the officials determined that the shot clock should not have reset and put 4 seconds on the clock.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Anthony (NYK) was inside the arc on his successful field goal was confirmed.
Nene (WAS) beats Thomas (NYK) to the spot (point of contact), giving him enough room to avoid the screen.
Lopez (NYK) moves his pivot foot heel to toe.
Dudley (WAS) holds Anthony (NYK) as he attempts to catch the pass.
Lopez (NYK) bumps Nene (WAS) with his forearm and the contact affects his shooting movement.
Porter (WAS) makes incidental contact with Thomas (NYK) as they attempt to rebound.
Nene (WAS) tangles with Lopez (NYK) affecting his movement.
Galloway (NYK) requests timeout before his foot goes out of bounds.
Nene (WAS) commits a take foul on Anthony (NYK).

[Observable in production angle] On drive, Thomas (NYK) makes no contact with Beal as he attempts his layup. LATR (across court) Lopez (NYK) remains vertical, turning slightly, absorbing contact and getting ball. Incidental contact occurs as Beal comes to his space.
Beal (WAS) commits a take foul on Anthony (NYK).
Wall (WAS) does not inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
Wall (WAS) commits a take foul on Galloway (NYK).
